abstract: Friends and family gather together to celebrate the life and career of Maggie Tabberer.
description: Featuring a variety of guests from all areas of Maggie Tabberer's diverse career up to the mid 1970s, viewers will be taken on an intimate journey. From revisiting her childhood with her long term friend, to meeting her husband and having children, through her career as a model and muse for Helmut Lang to her media roles on 'Beauty and the Beast' to her new career as a fashion designer.
